and for your club.

00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:08,335
Well, good for
all of us, right?

00:01:08,335 --> 00:01:10,804
This is not about the money
for me, bro.

00:01:10,804 --> 00:01:13,273
It's about the soul
of Cuba.

00:01:13,273 --> 00:01:14,374
The music.

00:01:14,374 --> 00:01:15,876
