00:01:17,878 --> 00:01:20,881
<i>Cuidado,</i> Vegas,
Silvana has arrived.

00:01:20,881 --> 00:01:22,349
Vegas is just
the beginning.

00:01:22,349 --> 00:01:23,350
Sure, sure, sure.

00:01:23,350 --> 00:01:24,651
<i>Necesitamos hablar</i> press.

00:01:24,651 --> 00:01:25,952
We do the local news,

00:01:25,952 --> 00:01:28,722
