Marta...!

00:01:39,599 --> 00:01:41,902
No!

00:01:41,902 --> 00:01:43,203
Oh, Marta...!

00:01:43,203 --> 00:01:44,838
(camera clicking)

00:01:44,838 --> 00:01:46,540
(indistinct radio communication,
sirens wailing in distance)

00:01:46,540 --> 00:01:47,541
Thank you.

00:01:47,541 --> 00:01:48,642
Hey, fellas,

00:01:48,642 --> 00:01:50,677
what do we got?
Marta Cuerto,

00:01:50,677 --> 00:01:53,313
32, Cuban national.

00:01:53,313 --> 00:01:55,682
Sister to
Silvana Cuerto,

00:01:55,682 --> 00:01:57,617
Cuban pop star.

00:01:57,617 --> 00:01:58,652
Who found the body?

00:01:58,652 --> 00:02:00,253
Silvana and her manager.

00:02:00,253 --> 00:02:03,657
So, no signs of
a disturbance.

00:02:03,657 --> 00:02:05,792
No blood, no cleanup,
which means

00:02:05,792 --> 00:02:07,294
this isn't the primary.

00:02:07,294 --> 00:02:10,630
The body was staged,
just like that,

00:02:10,630 --> 00:02:12,866
and one of Silvana's costumes

00:02:12,866 --> 00:02:14,000
was taken
off the rack

00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:16,403
and put
on the victim's body.

00:02:16,403 --> 00:02:19,239
That explains the lack
of blood on the dress.

00:02:19,239 --> 00:02:20,807
What do we got
going here, bud?

00:02:20,807 --> 00:02:24,811
Blunt force trauma-- the face
and most of her upper torso.

00:02:24,811 --> 00:02:28,348
Semicircular impressions
all over the body.

00:02:28,348 --> 00:02:31,585
(thermometer beeps)
Liver temp is 90.4.

00:02:31,585 --> 00:02:33,286
She died about six hours ago.

00:02:34,688 --> 00:02:36,523
I'll get the gurney.

00:02:36,523 --> 00:02:40,961
So our killer brings her here,
stages the body...

00:02:40,961 --> 00:02:42,662
nobody even notices?

00:02:42,662 --> 00:02:45,232
She was rehearsing
for a couple of hours onstage.

00:02:45,232 --> 00:02:47,868
The music's loud,
people are distracted.

00:02:47,868 --> 00:02:49,836
How many ways in and out
of here?
Only two.

00:02:49,836 --> 00:02:51,805
Door from the stage,
and there's a back door

00:02:51,805 --> 00:02:54,241
down that hallway
leading to the alley.

00:02:54,241 --> 00:02:56,409
Well, that's the how;
I'd like to know the why.

00:02:56,409 --> 00:02:57,611
Silvana's sister...

00:02:59,412 --> 00:03:03,250
...in her dress,
sitting at her vanity...

00:03:04,351 --> 00:03:06,686
...staring into her mirror.

00:03:11,958 --> 00:03:13,593
You got something?

00:03:13,593 --> 00:03:14,961
Yeah.

00:03:34,748 --> 00:03:36,683
<i>"Silvana, eres</i>
<i>la proxima"?</i>

00:03:38,652 --> 00:03:40,887
"Silvana, you're next."

